productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Ardeth has one of these. She works as a gasman and she says it looks fuzzy.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
My neighbor Lori has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks whopping.
